### GLOW Authentication API Test Suite
# Gunakan ekstensi REST Client di VSCode untuk menjalankan script ini.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 1. Register User Baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 2. Register Owner Baru (Akan membuat Business Profile)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Owner",
  "email": "testowner@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "OWNER",
  "businessName": "PT Test Pariwisata"
}

### 3. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "budi@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Dapatkan Profil Saat Ini (Requires Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Uji Coba Token Tidak Valid
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer token-asal-asalan-123
